import * as d3 from 'd3' import { useState, useEffect } from 'react' function Weight() { const [SvgWeight, setSvgWeight] = useState() useEffect(() => { const SvgWeightCreation = d3 .select('.weight-box') .append('svg') .attr('width', 825) .attr('height', 320) .append('p') .text('bananas') setSvgWeight(SvgWeightCreation) }, []) return
bananas}
} export default Weight
